         <abstract id="aspace_1312ebc39cfdfb8bfc707fab4fe1a04a">An artificial collection of correspondence, payrolls, pay tables, receipts, commissions, and miscellanea including documents from Connecticut, Massachusetts, New York, and South Carolina military forces.</abstract>
    
