      <scopecontent id="aspace_d7bc7c19332162a279a53aa9ad8ea875">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>An artificial collection of correspondence, payrolls, pay tables, receipts, commissions, and miscellanea including documents from Connecticut, Massachusetts, New York, and South Carolina military forces.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
